{"tid":420591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★2017 9-30 Apple又被訴訟！！！","createTime":"2017-10-01T13:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T03:02:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd890363e5f3616d71fb86738e405fba52927455","tid":420591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"根據外媒 ARS Technica 的報導，蘋果公司被一家位於北達科他州的、美洲土著部落所擁有的 MEC Resources 公司提起專利侵權訴訟，然而這家公司從未發明過類似平板電腦的產品<br />\n<br />\n今年 3 月份，總部位於德克薩斯州的 Prowire 提交了針對蘋果的原始專利訴訟。該公司指控稱，iPad 4 中使用的電感器侵犯了其「電磁干擾效應最小化的電感器」專利。這項專利最初是由台灣一家名為 Fuco Technology 的公司發明的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/tech/8bv6xg4.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Ftech%2F8bv6xg4.html&d=%2BaMW0YQM9Ssvo4nQqpn9j4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e31e250e\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/tech/8bv6xg4.html</a>"},{"pid":"540918910a7c515b1af47a5d7cd91d0ed9331ef9","tid":420591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"Apple Game Over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ae87b5d620cb8a9c3a55809639f324fd16d489","tid":420591,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf068fe99025bca14030b8e56fbdd1d23e25c6cd","tid":420591,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset